{
  "text": "However, the challenging problem of accuracy [CITATION_1] in describing BLA in conjugated systems, photochemical properties or static and dynamic electron correlation in analyzing π-conjugation in the ground and excited states will not be discussed further here (see recent work on 1,3-butadiene [CITATION_2] ).",
